# Graphify - Knowledge Graph for Codebases

**Installed via uv tool** (`graphify 0.9.3`)

```bash
graphify .                          # Build graph from current directory
graphify query "question"           # Query the graph
graphify path "A" "B"               # Find path between concepts
graphify explain "Concept"          # Explain a node
graphify export callflow-html       # Mermaid call-flow diagrams
graphify install --platform cline   # Install skill for Cline
graphify hook install               # Git hooks for auto-update
graphify watch ./src                # Auto-sync as files change
graphify add <url>                  # Add paper/video/doc to graph
```

**Outputs**: `graphify-out/graph.html`, `GRAPH_REPORT.md`, `graph.json`

